title: 76: Bachelor in Paradise: Week 6 (Part 11)

description:
BIP is coming to a close and The Broads discuss this episode filled with tough conversations and break ups. They chat Connor being blindsided, Demi’s vulnerability, the future of Chris and Katie, Tayshia’s prom, Blake being the Paradise pinata, go on numerous personal tangents (it’s been a while), and much more!
